reviewText: It was a good video to see how it all began.
If your a fan of prison break the/  this is for you. Lets you get to know the characters on a whole new level.
Love the show. Best series I've ever seen

Fantastic show with excellent writers, directors, and actors.  Edge of your seat action in every episode (hard to not binge watch when the episode ends with so much at stake) - looking forward to the new season!!!!
Loved it! Best show, cast and writers!!
Only thing missing is Wentworth Miller to make this interview perfect!

I was sorry Wentworth Miller and William Fichtner weren't there.  But it sure showed how much of a sense of humor Sarah Wayne Callies has, and it was nice to see Robert Knepper as he is.....very likeable.  He plays the creepiest character on the show.
I always enjoy interviews with casts. Learning little behind the scenes stuff. Good quality. Fun DVD if you're a fan of the show.
Not well organized. Not having Wentworth Miller was a big mistake.
My entire household loves Prison Break.  Enjoyed seeing the cast and creators discussing the show.  We can not wait for the new episodes in 2016.
